# Yabasic UI components

`components.json` uses Base UI (`"style": "base-nova"`). Primitives import `@base-ui/react/*`, not Radix.

**Add component (user runs):**  
`cd packages/yabasic && pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add https://basecn.dev/r/<name>.json`

Verify imports are `@base-ui/react/...`. Do not run install commands in-agent; see `user-run-commands.mdc`.
